1 Sec. 6. Proceeds. Resolved: That any proceeds from the sale or lease of all or
2 portions of the state property described in section 2 pursuant to this resolve must be used
3 to reimburse the Department of Administrative and Financial Services for administrative
4 expenses and be deposited into the department's Bureau of General Services capital repair
5 and improvement account for capital improvements.
6 Sec. 7. Repeal. Resolved: That the authorization to convey property granted by this
7 resolve is repealed 5 years from the effective date of this resolve.
